QuestData.Title: A Blow to Morale
QuestData.Description:
This place is the source of all of our corruption.
The kelfin are taken and broken here.
Hit them where it hurts. Break their power, kill every naga you see, wreak havoc!
Every little crack we make, weakens their foundation.
QuestData.LogDescription: Disrupt all activities in the Shirakess Repository.
